{"tid":1648724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解聽日開花一個post都冇？摺乜撚嘢紙？","createTime":"2019-10-12T10:32:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T14:17:35.000Z","uid":10521,"like":133,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"214d15bd7232124e780ad5bea5f29f58fdb3dbc5","tid":1648724,"uid":10521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:32:45.000Z","msg":"成日話少人少人，話人休息撚，轉頭文宣個波就射俾人<br />\n話冇大型遊行嗰啲，諗下一百萬二百萬用左幾耐時間吹雞？下下一兩日前叫，仲要得連登ig，大把人係靠睇連儂牆先知資訊，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地share一百次佢哋都唔會知</span></span><br />\n<br />\n總結：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大型遊行要預時間文宣</span></span>，就算你一兩前先講啲狗都一定快過你，倒不如早啲宣傳，人數一多大家都安全，至於係唔係港島定九龍可以再傾<br />\n<br />\n開花當然可以快閃，勇武當然自己決定行動，但和理唔得，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唱歌行街定集會要講</span></span>，唔係成班人出左去冇目的，效率低又危險<br />\n<br />\nBtw個摺紙post大家自己判斷，呢一兩日先彈出嚟，撞哂開花，唔係鬼就係on9<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後，求下大家唔好再抖，手足唔係condom</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zx5mCLX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzx5mCLX.jpg&h=51334c07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a49f739da4e6f791a56fd76eb67ec473b860efc","tid":1648724,"uid":46822,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:33:12.000Z","msg":"民意不會逆轉但會被消耗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">停止雨革無意義無重點鳩嗚式活動</span></span><br />\n每星期1-2個活動為宜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要有明確主題<br />\n和理非，勇武輪流上場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e84e55b637230d15ee768e1aef6282962b734935","tid":1648724,"uid":47659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:33:48.000Z","