span>，唔係成班人出左去冇目的，效率低又危險<br />\n<br />\nBtw個摺紙post大家自己判斷，呢一兩日先彈出嚟，撞哂開花，唔係鬼就係on9<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後，求下大家唔好再抖，手足唔係condom</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zx5mCLX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzx5mCLX.jpg&h=51334c07&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:17:41.000Z","msg":"Tui"}]}